what a programing language is.

00:55:51.651 --> 00:55:53.395
He says, well,waa
waa waa waa waa waa--

00:55:57.850 --> 00:56:01.780
So, I would, for this
gathered audience,

00:56:01.780 --> 00:56:04.822
I would say make good waa
waa waa waa waa waa waa waa.

