real moment that I recognize,

01:01:34.880 --> 01:01:36.620
which is that artists
are now having

01:01:36.620 --> 01:01:39.410
to do jobs and communicate
in ways and deal

01:01:39.410 --> 01:01:41.790
with stuff they didn't used to.

01:01:41.790 --> 01:01:46.050
And that, in itself,
isn't really discussed,

01:01:46.050 --> 01:01:47.420
how we juggle that.

01:01:47.420 --> 01:01:50.270
And I think that's interesting
stuff to talk about.

01:01:50.270 --> 01:01:52.060
And usually it
doesn't get that deep.

01:01:52.060 --> 01:01:53.560
ALAN LIGHT: It's a
remarkable piece.

